title: Paul Garatrenda 10/19: NBA, Rachel Levine, Kanye, Dr. Fauci, Southwest, A. Rod, Steve Martin
itunes:title: Paul Garatrenda 10/19: NBA, Rachel Levine, Kanye, Dr. Fauci, Southwest, A. Rod, Steve Martin
description:
In this edition of Paul Garatrenda, Jack and Miles discuss NBA tip-off day, Rachel Levine being selected assistant health secretary, Kanye's mask and name change, Dr. Fauci NOT doing that thing people said he did, Southwest folding on vaccine mandates, Red Sox fans' ruthless taunts for A Rod, and Steve Martin's performance in 'Only Murders in the Building'
